Ing '''Southern Leyte State University''' (SLSU) metung yang unibersidad a pangmaldang (public university) miyayampang miyayaliwang titulung pang-kolehiyu (college degrees). Ing sadiang Southern Leyte State College of Science and Technology, megi yang unibersidad a pang-estadu kapamilatan ning Republic Act 9261 kanitang [[Marzu 7]], [[2004]]. 

*Deti reng limang campus a bibilug king unibersidad
**[[Sogod]] - Main Campus - makatutuk ya kareng kursu king siensia ampong teknolohiya
** [[Hinunangan]] - makatutuk ya king negosiung pang-agrikultura (agricultural entrepreneurship) 
** [[Tomas Oppus]] - makatutuk ya king pamagsane rang akademiku deng talaturu (teacher education) 
** [[San Juan]] - makatutuk ya king komersiu ampong pamanibala (business and administration) 
** [[Bontoc]] - makatutuk ya king pamipasulung king pamanasan (fishery development)

